\begin{array}{l}  {S_n} = 1 + \frac{1}{{2 \cdot 2}} + \frac{1}{{3 \cdot 3}} + ...\frac{1}{{n \cdot n}} <  \\   1 + \frac{1}{{2 \cdot 1}} + \frac{1}{{3 \cdot 2}} + ... +  + \frac{1}{{n \cdot (n - 1)}} =  \\   1 + \left( {1 - \frac{1}{2}} \right) + \left( {\frac{1}{2} - \frac{1}{{3 \cdot 2}}} \right) + ... + \left( {\frac{1}{{n - 1}} - \frac{1}{n}} \right) \\    = 1 + 1 - \frac{1}{n} < 2 \\   \end{array}
\frac{1}{{n \cdot (n - 1)}}=\frac{1}{{n-1}}-\frac{1}{{n }}
